{"questionId":"35033816","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The following diagram shows a park bounded by a fence in the shape of a quadrilateral <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>ABCD</mtext></math>. A straight path crosses through the park from <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>B</mtext></math> to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>D</mtext></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>AB</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>85</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>m</mtext><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mtext>AD</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>85</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>m</mtext><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mtext>BC</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>40</mn><mo> </mo><mtext>m</mtext><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mtext>C</mtext><mover><mtext>B</mtext><mo>^</mo></mover><mtext>D</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>41</mn><mo>°</mo><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mtext>B</mtext><mover><mtext>C</mtext><mo>^</mo></mover><mtext>D</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>120</mn><mo>°</mo></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/cf5c1f3d8dceb95dbd0d989858e69331e40cc87e.png\"></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Write down the value of angle <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>BDC</mtext></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>19</mn><mo>°</mo></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"35033816","referenceCode":"22N.2.SL.TZ0.2a.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down the value of angle BDC.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Prior learning"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}